snippet.title: Best VGM 1999 - Shenmue - FREE 1 (Walking Theme 1)
snippet.description:

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Dreamcast
Shenmue (1999)
FREE 1
Osamu Murata, Ryuji Iuchi, Takenobu Mitsuyoshi, Takeshi Yanagawa & Yuzo Koshiro
